snippet: The American Steamer Baltic, Captain COMSTOCK, arrived at this port yesterday morning. She left Liverpool on the 14th. We are indebted to the Purser of the Baltic for the prompt delivery of English papers....
lead_paragraph: The American Steamer Baltic, Captain COMSTOCK, arrived at this port yesterday morning. She left Liverpool on the 14th. We are indebted to the Purser of the Baltic for the prompt delivery of English papers.
